{"tid":440814,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我究竟係咪冇腦？","createTime":"2017-10-19T06:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T17:21:01.000Z","uid":154603,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d572987f44c8f94bf0135f81c8582c180766d5","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:13:35.000Z","msg":"份人好冇記性，成日自己講過咩做過咩都唔記得，次次要人提先恍然大悟，久而久之覺得自己好冇用，個腦好似裝屎咁<br />\n<br />\n唔知係自己份人冇自信定冇腦，平地一啲自己熟悉嘅嘢，會好地地產生疑惑唔肯定個答案，例如明知今日係星期四，人地問我今日星期幾，我會唔肯定個答案，然後睇下日曆......個腦好似冇用咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔知點解對身邊事物好唔敏感，好多時都係後知後覺，同社會步伐不一致，睇住身邊嘅人慢慢進步，我就原地踏步<br />\n<br />\n我覺得思維方面都有問題，成日問埋啲問題其實係人都知，但係我就唔知然後重新問一次，搞到人地會覺得我好蠢<br />\n<br />\n事實上我覺得自己真係好蠢，係一堆人入面基本上冇乜建設，讀書又廢，份人又懶，而家搵唔到自己有咩價值，係一條廢柴，以上事情間唔中就做一次，每次都覺得自己廢到冇人有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實，我究竟係冇腦，定係冇自信份人唔積極？嘗試做多啲運動會唔會改善到？<br />\n<br />\n唉，其實有冇人係好似我咁樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6009d1447a0b3215bf63867dbf9a2fd0636111b8","tid":440814,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"接觸多啲人 接觸個社會 慢慢你個腦就會快 你慣咗唔用 佢就唔識行"},{"pid":"201face291e778e38f019f4c81a2b2326569b8a2","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:20:51.000Z","msg":"識我嘅唔該當睇唔到個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2eccc12cf2477644edc5d3e502f50227b5d5eb8","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>接觸多啲人 接觸個社會 慢慢你個腦就會快 你慣咗唔用 佢就唔識行</blockquote><br />\n之前返過份office工，嗰一排份人的確係轉得快咗，感覺到自己係做到嘢，但一返到屋企就打回原形，好hea，而家開學之後更加不知所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157cc2760d73191ab0a1d8e7367c5830aead417b","tid":440814,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:29:31.000Z","msg":"up乜"},{"pid":"3a717c4ca1c9263881c58ec0aae88b5ef7fe66e5","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>up乜</blockquote><br />\n原來已經去到語無倫次階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc59596545b9eb5090340a61e6d46f317245cad1","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184dfd583e3d68011cf8bbfcb3e0e84e157df51f","tid":440814,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"懶加冇自信 然後錯完驚再錯就更加冇自信 無限loop"},{"pid":"d6ae491b9bd7417f5b1ec45ddd4c6563808c2f34","tid":440814,"uid":86337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"我自己一個人果時就諗得好快<br />\n<br />\n係人地面前個腦就死左機咁"},{"pid":"4d45ecd6d254405872ad1ca784685f7381ad3b02","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>懶加冇自信 然後錯完驚再錯就更加冇自信 無限loop</blockquote><br />\n好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1faeb4ac86a4542e176f1530a2fd278626b962f4","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己一個人果時就諗得好快<br />\n<br />\n係人地面前個腦就死左機咁</blockquote><br />\n我人前人後都係死機狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4879a264268416805b1b29e9c3060221011371","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>懶加冇自信 然後錯完驚再錯就更加冇自信 無限loop</blockquote><br />\n好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以點改善 比啲指引我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53168e310d641f6846e0355e054b2952ba9ced1","tid":440814,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:10:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>懶加冇自信 然後錯完驚再錯就更加冇自信 無限loop</blockquote><br />\n好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以點改善 比啲指引我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無記性果d 可以試下有重要野記果陣抄低佢 求其開電話打落memo都得<br />\n<br />\n至於點先有自信d咪見多d人 做下運動<br />\n再唔係返下pt囉 你自己都話返工會冇咁鈍"},{"pid":"4f07e05fd2ce0b35cf2a2be4bb87a5bfc1788d3b","tid":440814,"uid":41315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:12:36.000Z","msg":"好簡單姐<br />\n因為你平時都無去思考<br />\n所有野得過且過<br />\n有時間又唔去睇多啲書<br />\n平時亦都無真正細心咁去留意身邊既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b85ce76c5db5ab8b83e44c8e03d44642d3af5a","tid":440814,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"同我幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係記性好差 乜都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5198d12db48475aa9da6562267c39db45fc20ffb","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係記性好差 乜都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇user name都知同病相憐"},{"pid":"bb509899070e114dce8b9667996e04bcfe082296","tid":440814,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:43:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同我幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係記性好差 乜都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇user name都知同病相憐</blockquote><br />\n去書局睇下書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有助大腦開發我認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd88df3acc81fc3b518e4cc9375be405d854b0d9","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:44:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同我幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係記性好差 乜都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇user name都知同病相憐</blockquote><br />\n去書局睇下書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有助大腦開發我認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇話睇咩類型書會幫助大啲？"},{"pid":"aa7f6aed6e779e3cfa3b14e846d6138cd6ebb4b7","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好簡單姐<br />\n因為你平時都無去思考<br />\n所有野得過且過<br />\n有時間又唔去睇多啲書<br />\n平時亦都無真正細心咁去留意身邊既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n100%中point<br />\n我覺得自己好少進入緊張狀態 一緊張起嚟其實個人其實清醒好多冇咁渾噩<br />\n但永遠都缺乏動力去做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47da5119f4b6ce2f40930d3495d522da6d5724b2","tid":440814,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同我幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係記性好差 乜都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇user name都知同病相憐</blockquote><br />\n去書局睇下書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有助大腦開發我認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇話睇咩類型書會幫助大啲？</blockquote><br />\n答你唔到<br />\n但可以俾啲建議你<br />\n<br />\n搵1個鐘時間<br />\n唔好短過1小時, 當係挑戰又好咩都好<br />\n鍾意既可以帶多 100蚊<br />\n<br />\n真係收工/放學去最近既書局行下<br />\n唔好圖書館, 你呢類人會厭啲書舊唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去心理學果區, 開始計時 1個鐘<br />\n你覺得邊本書名岩你, 又或者封面靚既<br />\n又或者覺得對你有用既, 就拎上手睇<br />\n打書釘唔洗錢<br />\n唔岩既就搵過另一本<br />\n覺得深既就搵日本翻譯既書, 一般會淺白啲<br />\n<br />\n直到計時結束都唔准離開 心理學果區<br />\n意猶未盡就用100蚊買左佢"},{"pid":"f87041174de192d242dcf318f211a67773e71f03","tid":440814,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好簡單姐<br />\n因為你平時都無去思考<br />\n所有野得過且過<br />\n有時間又唔去睇多啲書<br />\n平時亦都無真正細心咁去留意身邊既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n100%中point<br />\n我覺得自己好少進入緊張狀態 一緊張起嚟其實個人其實清醒好多冇咁渾噩<br />\n但永遠都缺乏動力去做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n動力既野<br />\n有時唔多唔少都係迫出黎<br />\n曾經有一段時間<br />\n我迫自己每日只要有時間<br />\n就算只有 1個鐘都好<br />\n都要最少帶1本書, 去自修室坐<br />\n<br />\n我當時係咁樣諗<br />\n坐係屋企我只會玩電話上網無左成日時間又學唔到野<br />\n去到自修室就算我睇完 15分鐘書訓 45分鐘<br />\n我都賺左15分鐘"},{"pid":"0f374efa5959eab9da8fb6f52e0648f66b81504c","tid":440814,"uid":151833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:09:37.000Z","msg":"記唔記得你上一個留言講左咩？"},{"pid":"c4850254d563c265daa1fd01f19a4a02473c615b","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同我幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係記性好差 乜都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇user name都知同病相憐</blockquote><br />\n去書局睇下書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有助大腦開發我認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇話睇咩類型書會幫助大啲？</blockquote><br />\n答你唔到<br />\n但可以俾啲建議你<br />\n<br />\n搵1個鐘時間<br />\n唔好短過1小時, 當係挑戰又好咩都好<br />\n鍾意既可以帶多 100蚊<br />\n<br />\n真係收工/放學去最近既書局行下<br />\n唔好圖書館, 你呢類人會厭啲書舊唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去心理學果區, 開始計時 1個鐘<br />\n你覺得邊本書名岩你, 又或者封面靚既<br />\n又或者覺得對你有用既, 就拎上手睇<br />\n打書釘唔洗錢<br />\n唔岩既就搵過另一本<br />\n覺得深既就搵日本翻譯既書, 一般會淺白啲<br />\n<br />\n直到計時結束都唔准離開 心理學果區<br />\n意猶未盡就用100蚊買左佢</blockquote><br />\n好實用 希望我做得到！<br />\nbtw我反而係咩都無所謂嗰類人，睇舊書冇問題<br />\n本身自己買過兩本心理書 但封咗塵<br />\n係時候拎出嚟睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4c1a4aea2f3f3154a97791602c89f1714c19ac","tid":440814,"uid":154603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記唔記得你上一個留言講左咩？</blockquote><br />\n要不是有紀錄 可能唔記得"},{"pid":"98d84a46db9dcfd3e49e1f8a2ba35053965d3dba","tid":440814,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同我幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係記性好差 乜都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇user name都知同病相憐</blockquote><br />\n去書局睇下書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有助大腦開發我認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇話睇咩類型書會幫助大啲？</blockquote><br />\n答你唔到<br />\n但可以俾啲建議你<br />\n<br />\n搵1個鐘時間<br />\n唔好短過1小時, 當係挑戰又好咩都好<br />\n鍾意既可以帶多 100蚊<br />\n<br />\n真係收工/放學去最近既書局行下<br />\n唔好圖書館, 你呢類人會厭啲書舊唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去心理學果區, 開始計時 1個鐘<br />\n你覺得邊本書名岩你, 又或者封面靚既<br />\n又或者覺得對你有用既, 就拎上手睇<br />\n打書釘唔洗錢<br />\n唔岩既就搵過另一本<br />\n覺得深既就搵日本翻譯既書, 一般會淺白啲<br />\n<br />\n直到計時結束都唔准離開 心理學果區<br />\n意猶未盡就用100蚊買左佢</blockquote><br />\n好實用 希望我做得到！<br />\nbtw我反而係咩都無所謂嗰類人，睇舊書冇問題<br />\n本身自己買過兩本心理書 但封咗塵<br />\n係時候拎出嚟睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好拖<br />\n唔好俾藉口自己<br />\n你每日出門帶埋本書出去啦<br />\n搭車睇2頁"}]}